The paper also focuses on reducing sample complexity, which is a common problem in reinforcement learning, and proposes a new approach to address this issue. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks, which suggests that it may belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes a new algorithm for reinforcement learning, which suggests that it may also belong to the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
